title: Dave East Interview and More
itunes:title: Dave East Interview and More
description:
Tuesday 8/22- Today on the show we had rapper and eye candy Dave East come to the show where he spoke about his new album Paranoia, Christina Millian, modeling and more. Also, since the volume of calls have gone up for “Shoot Your Shot” we had more listeners call up today, and this time a listener tried to shoot their shot at their ex, after having a baby by someone else. Moreover, Charlamagne gave “Donkey of the Day” to young ladies who wore an “Make America Great Again” shirt, and out of all places at an HBCU “Howard University”.
